name: Andersen-s-first-show
tagline: Codes to things, And's first milestone.
body:
The following paragraphs seem to be a part of the web's brief introduction:
It's my pleasure to build my first web program,
and I wish that with the accumulation of my knowledge and experience,
these pages will be decorated much better than ever before.

                                                   Andersen
                                                 Mar.9th 2016
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
